videos.description: Duncan Robinson has some space and knocks down a 3-pointer for Michigan's first basket.
videos.headline: Robinson breaks Wolverines' cold streak with 3-pointer

videos.description: Muhammad-Ali  Abdur-Rahkman makes a cut in the lane and finishes with a huge slam.
videos.headline: Abdur-Rahkman rocks the rim for the Wolverines

videos.description: Michigan's Muhammad-Ali Abdur-Rahkman throws it up up and over Texas' Mohamed Bamba for the tough bucket.
videos.headline: Abdur-Rahkman gets the bucket over the reach of Bamba

videos.description: Mohamed Bamba shows off his vertical making this alley-oop look easy.
videos.headline: Bamba gets up for slam

videos.description: Mo Wagner swings the momentum for the Wolverines with two 3-pointers to extend the lead.
videos.headline: Wagner knocks down back-to-back 3-pointers

videos.description: Kerwin Roach hits a deep 3-pointer for the Longhorns.
videos.headline: Roach knocks down deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Muhammad-Ali Abdur-Rahkman uses the glass as the shot clock is winding down.
videos.headline: Abdur-Rahkman banks in desperation 3-pointer
